data.description: Great looking home needs a little TLC but not much Sold As Is. All Bedrooms are up. Amazing curb appeal in sought after community of Stonefield. This home features 4 bed, 2.5 bath, natural light throughout, open floorplan, custom shutters in living room and master bedroom, all bedrooms up with office space downstairs overlooking backyard oasis with Heated POOL and Jacuzzi perfect for endless entertaining. Home has brand new Solar screens on all windows.  Also you have extra storage shed in backyard!
